g Lusi to regret her involvement. Ultimately, the fourteenth prince plotted to assassinate Yongzheng with the help of Zeng Jing and Lusi, igniting a fierce battle.","tmdb":{"type":"tv","id":"87673","season":1,"vote_average":0,"vote_count":0},"modified":"2024-11-07T09:30:50.000Z","cast":["Alex Man Chi-Leung","Lương Tiểu Long","Trương Quốc Vinh","Bonnie Ngai Chau-Wah","Kong To","Jimmy Wong Shu-Kei","Cheng Chu-Fung","La Lạc Lâm","Hoàng Nhất Phi","Newton Lai Hon-Chi","Iris Ma Man-Yee","Văn Tuyết Nhi","Chan Chik-Wai","Miu Kam-Fung","Yung Wai-Man"],"director":[],"cast_meta":[{"name":"Alex Man Chi-Leung","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Alex Man Chi-Leung","tmdb_id":148886,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/jY5DKV1oioxxhD2xZdjBJPqVa8.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/148886"},{"name":"Lương Tiểu Long","name_vi":"Lương Tiểu Long","name_original":"Bruce Leung Siu-Lung","tmdb_id":83491,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/thgf1TvGZu8Zmpd2enLaPWsqcXb.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/83491"},{"name":"Trương Quốc Vinh","name_vi":"Trương Quốc Vinh","name_original":"Leslie Cheung","tmdb_id":69637,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/xdSUevukGCrayOdLd4Kd6YSJnKR.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/69637"},{"name":"Bonnie Ngai Chau-Wah","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Bonnie Ngai Chau-Wah","tmdb_id":1615858,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/hTL1xg40jaUBF5aQbJAOSCfKBo3.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1615858"},{"name":"Kong To","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Kong To","tmdb_id":3800360,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/m2Pxjjtlx76wQj730WBfsC1oDsx.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/3800360"},{"name":"Jimmy Wong Shu-Kei","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Jimmy Wong Shu-Kei","tmdb_id":548328,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/8rOKeupd2QE90TX03okFSA7MzPW.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/548328"},{"name":"Cheng Chu-Fung","name_vi":null,"name_orig